{
  "title": "ISic001111. Record of construction work on the agora",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ἱερ<span class=\"underline\">οθ</span>υτέοντος <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φάωνος\n                    Νύμφωνος Σωπολιανοῦ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φάωνος\">Φάωνος</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νύμφωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Νύμφωνος\">Νύ[μ]<span class=\"underline\">φ</span>ωνος</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σωπολιανοῦ\">Σωπολιανοῦ</span></span>, <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ἀγορα̣νομέοντος <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ξενάρχου\n                    Ἀπολλοδώρου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ξενάρχου\">Ξενάρχου</span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀπολλοδώρου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ἀπολλοδώρου\">Ἀπολλ<span class=\"underline\">οδώ</span>ρου</span></span></span> καὶ τὰν ἐπιμέλειαν <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>πο<span class=\"underline\">ι&lt;η&gt;σαμ</span>ένου τῶν ἔργων vacat <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ἁ ἀ̣[γ]<span class=\"underline\">ο</span>[ρ]<span class=\"underline\">ὰ</span> κατεσκευάσθη </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΙΕΡ<span class=\"underline\">ΟΘ</span>ΥΤΕΟΝΤΟΣ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φάωνος\n                    Νύμφωνος Σωπολιανοῦ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φάωνος\">ΦΑΩΝΟΣ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νύμφωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Νύμφωνος\">ΝΥ[.]<span class=\"underline\">Φ</span>ΩΝΟΣ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σωπολιανοῦ\">ΣΩΠΟΛΙΑΝΟΥ</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΑΓΟΡ.ΝΟΜΕΟΝΤΟΣ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ξενάρχου\n                    Ἀπολλοδώρου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ξενάρχου\">ΞΕΝΑΡΧΟΥ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀπολλοδώρου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ἀπολλοδώρου\">ΑΠΟΛΛ<span class=\"underline\">ΟΔΩ</span>ΡΟΥ</span></span></span>ΚΑΙΤΑΝΕΠΙΜΕΛΕΙΑΝ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΠΟ<span class=\"underline\">ΙΣΑΜ</span>ΕΝΟΥΤΩΝΕΡΓΩΝVACAT<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>Α.[.]<span class=\"underline\">Ο</span>[.]<span class=\"underline\">Α</span>ΚΑΤΕΣΚΕΥΑΣΘΗ</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Ampolo and Erdas 2019</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The inscription, prior to discovery of the left hand fragment, was regularly cited in discussion of gymnasia evidence, due to the proposed restoration of the word xystos in line 6.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 40.1717 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 62.0684 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Gualtherus 1624 263 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388</a>  </li><li> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] 322 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931</a>  </li><li> Franz 1853 5546 and p.1249 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">290</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Hoffmann 1904 5189 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817</a></li><li> Dubois 1989 <a href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">215</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187</a></li><li> Nenci 1991 923 n.16-17 tav.297 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001413\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001413</a></li><li> De Vido 1991 972-973 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001409\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001409</a></li><li> Di Veroli 1996 310 n.5 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001476\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001476</a></li><li> De Vido 2003 397-398 no.4 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002041\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002041</a></li><li> Ampolo and Erdas 2019 G10 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Broad, finely carved letters. Alpha with straight bar, epsilon with shorter middle bar, theta, omicron, omega all smaller and above the line; theta possibly with central dot rather than cross-bar; kappa with short arms; Mu with vertical outer strokes, shorter inner strokes; pi without overlap of the horizontal; sigma with parallel outer strokes, phi with small eye and extended vertical; omega small, circular and open.</p> Line 1-6  29-40  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
